    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏描述：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在 <i>Snake King</i> 中夺取王位吧，这是一款令人耳目一新的经典贪吃蛇游戏！在这款复古风格的街机游戏中，您将引导您的蛇穿过一个简单的开放式竞技场，吞食水果，每次咬一口都会变长。但您长得越长，就越难避免撞到竞技场墙壁或自己的尾巴。随着速度和长度的增加，每一步都很重要！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/356ef128b0c7dde8f09eb94051c81308.poster.avif?t=1737958241\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/356ef128b0c7dde8f09eb94051c81308.webm?t=1737958241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/356ef128b0c7dde8f09eb94051c81308.mp4?t=1737958241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>经典贪吃蛇游戏玩法</strong>：目标很简单 — 吃水果，让蛇长大，避免与墙壁或自己相撞。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>水果与成长</strong>：收集散落在竞技场各处的水果，让蛇变长。吃得越多，游戏就越大，难度也就越大。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>得分和最高分</strong>：在玩游戏时跟踪当前得分，并尝试在每场新游戏中打破个人最高分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可自定义的蛇</strong>：解锁并为蛇选择不同的皮肤和颜色，让您个性化您的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/52ec99ff1783f613761151faf39b5d19.avif?t=1737958241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras_big/52ec99ff1783f613761151faf39b5d19.avif?t=1737958241 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/c62f48d20a0c58ac9a7a27eb2d00f5ee.avif?t=1737958241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras_big/c62f48d20a0c58ac9a7a27eb2d00f5ee.avif?t=1737958241 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/89ef71b60e2fbd45dcc8ebf1da642b8f.avif?t=1737958241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras_big/89ef71b60e2fbd45dcc8ebf1da642b8f.avif?t=1737958241 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras/9dd5a17db64c8b681a368bfdd7ab701e.avif?t=1737958241\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300910/extras_big/9dd5a17db64c8b681a368bfdd7ab701e.avif?t=1737958241 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>游戏玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <i>Snake King</i> 中，您可以通过简单的箭头键移动来控制蛇，在开放的竞技场中穿行，收集水果并变长。随着蛇的成长，躲避自己的身体变得越来越困难，速度的增加也增加了难度。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借其怀旧的游戏玩法、易于学习的控制和具有挑战性的进程，<i>Snake King</i> 提供了无尽的乐趣。你能打破最高分并成为终极蛇王吗？</p>",
